{
  "texts": [
    "The findings highlight the need for comprehensive approaches to teaching STEM subjects, ensuring that educators are well-equipped to handle the complexities of modern STEM curricula.",
    "STEAM integration.",
    "As STEM education continues to evolve, there is an increasing recognition of the importance of integrating the arts (STEAM) to foster creativity and innovation alongside technical skills.",
    "The transition from STEM to STEAM is gaining traction globally, emphasizing the value of a more holistic approach to education (Mejias et al. 2021).",
    "STEAM not only reinforces the traditional STEM disciplines but also encourages critical thinking, problem-solving, and creative expression, which are essential for addressing complex real-world challenges."
  ]
}